        {
            "title": "中石化首季純利按年增長26.9% 受惠油價上升及煉油副產品價差好轉",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中國石化(00386)公布，今年首季按國際會計準則的股東應佔利潤，達177.39億元(人民幣．下同)，按年增長26.9%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中石化官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/bplib_20230712-100717_source-web_SINOPEC_00386-1_source-web_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中石化官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/bplib_20230712-100717_source-web_SINOPEC_00386-1_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：中石化官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">若按中國會計準則，期內營業收入7066.95億元，按年倒退3.9%。歸屬上市公司股東淨利潤170.06億元，較去年同期升28.2%；扣除非經常性損益的歸屬上市公司股東淨利潤，也有170.87億元，按年升29.2%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">首季利潤總額242.06億元，按年升32.6%，主要是原油價格上行帶來庫存增利，以及煉油副產品價差好轉等因素導致。經營活動使用現金流淨額達55.58億元，則因為國際油價上漲，公司套期保值業務保證金支出增加，再加上庫存等佔用上升所影響。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15935910-%e4%b8%ad%e7%9f%b3%e5%8c%96%e9%a6%96%e5%ad%a3%e7%b4%94%e5%88%a9%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e5%a2%9e%e9%95%b726-9-%e5%8f%97%e6%83%a0%e6%b2%b9%e5%83%b9%e4%b8%8a%e5%8d%87%e5%8f%8a%e7%85%89%e6%b2%b9%e5%89%af",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/20240411_FI_source-web_00386-2.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-29 08:31:51",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "中國太保首季淨利按年增長4.3% 壽險新業務價值增9.6%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中國太保(02601)公布，今年首季淨利潤達100.41億元(人民幣．下同)，按年增長4.3%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中國太保2024年度可持續發展報告\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250515_FI_source-web_02601-2024-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中國太保2024年度可持續發展報告\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250515_FI_source-web_02601-2024-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：中國太保2024年度可持續發展報告</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">期內扣除非經常性損益的淨利潤為95.19億元，則較去年同期減少1.1%。實現保險服務收入702.34億元，按年升1%，其中太保壽險實現保險服務收入215.71億元，增長2.6%；太保產險實現保險服務收入477.72億元，則按年跌0.2%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">太保壽險首季期繳規模與價值實現雙升，實現規模保費1162.77億元，新保期繳規模保費189.29億元，按年增長41.4%；新業務價值63.72億元，增長9.6%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">太保產險期內實現原保險保費收入63.028億元，按年倒退0.3%。其中車險原保險保費收入268.71億元，增長0.1%，保費規模保持穩定；非車險原保險保費收入361.57億元，按年跌0.5%。承保綜合成本率為96.4%，較去年同期優化1個百分點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15935896-%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e5%a4%aa%e4%bf%9d%e9%a6%96%e5%ad%a3%e6%b7%a8%e5%88%a9%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e5%a2%9e%e9%95%b74-3-%e5%a3%bd%e9%9a%aa%e6%96%b0%e6%a5%ad%e5%8b%99%e5%83%b9%e5%80%bc%e5%a2%9e9-6",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250515_FI_source-web_02601-2024-2.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-29 08:21:48",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "黑期高水逾140點 重磅港股ADR大多偏強",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">新加坡黑期於今早約8時13升114點或0.45%，報25820點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股ADR指數報25730點，較香港上日現貨收市高50點或0.2%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">騰訊(00700)ADR收市折合每股港幣474.4元，較上日香港收市高0.59元或0.12%；阿里巴巴(09988)ADR收市折合每股港幣128.2元，較上日香港收市高1.67元或1.32%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">美團(03690)ADR收市折合每股港幣80.4元，較上日香港收市高0.14元或0.17%；京東(09618)ADR收市折合每股港幣116.5元，較上日香港收市高1.18元或1.03%；小米(01810)ADR收市折合每股港幣29.9元，較上日香港收市低0.01%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：騰訊官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-101229__source-web_00700.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：騰訊官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-101229__source-web_00700.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：騰訊官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滙控(00005)ADR收市折合每股港幣141元，較上日香港收市高0.4元或0.29%；友邦(01299)ADR收市折合每股港幣83.4元，較上日香港收市高0.22元或0.27%；港交所(00388)ADR收市折合每股港幣407.3元，較上日香港收市低0.28元或0.07%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230829_FI_source-web_HSBC-sign-Paris.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230829_FI_source-web_HSBC-sign-Paris.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：滙控官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中國平安(02318)ADR收市折合每股港幣61元，較上日香港收市高0.99元或1.65%；建設銀行(00939)ADR收市折合每股港幣8.9元，較上日香港收市高0.02元或0.22%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒指期貨夜市收報25762點，升55點，較上日恒指收市25679點，高水82點。科指期貨夜市收報4861點，較上日科指收市高水34點；國指期貨夜市收報8699點，較上日國指收市高水54點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15935900-%e9%bb%91%e6%9c%9f%e9%ab%98%e6%b0%b4%e9%80%be140%e9%bb%9e-%e9%87%8d%e7%a3%85%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1adr%e5%a4%a7%e5%a4%9a%e5%81%8f%e5%bc%b7",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/ADR-1_source-bp_-2-1.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-29 08:20:17",
