            "title": "兗礦能源首季純利按年增長42.14% 扣除非經常性損益則跌61.14%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">兗礦能源(01171)公布，今年首季歸屬上市公司股東淨利潤達39.55億元，較去年同期調整後數字增長42.14%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"兗礦能源官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/01171-Web2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"兗礦能源官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/01171-Web2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">兗礦能源官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">上述盈利提升，主要因為期內公開掛牌轉讓鑫泰全部股權，導致歸屬上市公司股東淨利潤按年提升28.43億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">事實上，扣除非經常性損益的歸屬上市公司股東淨利潤只得10.6億元，按年倒退61.14%，主要因為煤炭產品盈利按年減少。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15933402-%e5%85%97%e7%a4%a6%e8%83%bd%e6%ba%90%e9%a6%96%e5%ad%a3%e7%b4%94%e5%88%a9%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e5%a2%9e%e9%95%b742-14-%e6%89%a3%e9%99%a4%e9%9d%9e%e7%b6%93%e5%b8%b8%e6%80%a7%e6%90%8d%e7%9b%8a%e5%89%87",
